item.title: CVE-2019-10320|2024-08-04T22:17:20.390Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20credentials%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Credentials Plugin 2.1.18 and earlier allowed users with permission to create or update credentials to confirm the existence of files on the Jenkins master with an attacker-specified path, and obtain the certificate content of files containing a PKCS#12 certificate.
